-- MOVES-Zurich Life Singapore names Jamie McNish as sales chief
-- By Anet Josline Pinto in Bangalore
-- Thu Sep 25, 2014 08:04AM EDT
-- None



Sept 25 (Reuters) - Zurich Life Singapore, a part of Zurich Insurance Group <ZURN.VX>, said it appointed Jamie McNish to the newly created role of chief sales officer, effective Dec. 15.

McNish will report to Peter Huber, chief executive of Zurich's Life business in Singapore. He joins from Friends Provident International, where he was the regional director responsible for managing the sales teams in the Middle East and Africa.